track.name: Pipeline
comments: interesting and thought provoking ... likes it
I like everything Monolake does except for poop.
Br1g1tt3: nice image - really fits this awesome track...

Hypnotic. Imagine a broad highway at night. You're almost alone. Dark skies surround you and the only thing you see are stars, the occasional headlight of another car and the light of your car stereo. You drive on and on, sun rises and slowly you see the landscape take shape around you. A big plain were pipelines cross the road. Every now and then a strange looking factory, were pipes go up and down, some steam blows in the bright blue skie. And you drive and drive and drive. Only to be driving. Nowhere to go.
Sounds like there's influence from early FSOL, which is clearly a great thing.
